    "text": "This is an empty state description that appears when no MCP servers are connected. It instructs the user to connect servers in the settings to use them with the AI Agent. `{{mcpServers}}` refers to \"MCP servers\", `{{productName}}` is the product's brand name, and `{{aiAgent}}` is the AI Agent feature.",
